      "content": {
        "title": "Murmur Timing in the Cardiac Cycle",
        "definition": "Association of heart murmurs with specific cycle phases: systolic (aortic stenosis, mitral regurgitation) vs diastolic (aortic regurgitation, mitral stenosis).",
